Comment: 0,0:00:59.04,0:00:59.08,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,出现钟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.66,0:01:09.05,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Fate doom and future　dark over light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.76,0:01:12.26,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru (get out get out get out get out)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.26,0:01:14.51,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.51,0:01:17.18,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru (get out get out get out get out)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.18,0:01:19.56,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.56,0:01:24.94,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,錆びついた　shadow prison　姿潜めて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.94,0:01:29.49,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,行き場を探しては　I keep my soul in you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.49,0:01:32.03,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,So break out so break out -> To battle the tension
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.03,0:01:34.28,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Never give up that fight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.28,0:01:36.83,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,So break out so break out -> To battle the tension
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.83,0:01:39.50,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Don't let it claim your light rise
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.50,0:01:44.33,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,果てなきを彷徨う　飽く無き声が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.33,0:01:49.21,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,足枷を解いて　羽ばたくの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.21,0:01:52.01,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,時間の狭間で召されてく魂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.01,0:01:54.47,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,たとえ全てを焼き尽くされたとし
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.47,0:01:59.14,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,ても　飲み込んで　しまえば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.14,0:02:04.02,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,闇を振り翳して　胸に宿すアンサー
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:06.65,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1370,27)}闇中反転　照らして
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.65,0:02:09.03,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H0000FF&\3a&HFF&\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1365.333,91.001)}Aren't you? 明鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.65,0:02:09.03,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FF&\3c&H0000FF&\3a&HFF&\pos(1370.666,35)}Won't you make yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.65,0:02:09.03,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1720,74.668)} -> 探すの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.03,0:02:11.24,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,君を守りたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.24,0:02:13.86,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,そのに呼びかけるから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.86,0:02:18.83,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,闇中宣戦　全身全霊　生きてゆく証
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.86,0:02:18.83,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fs31\pos(1184,80)\bord1.2}climb back up unswayed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.83,0:02:21.41,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru(get out get out get out get out)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.41,0:02:23.79,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru
